These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: funk, classical, hip-hop, rock, d&b, salsa
6 different pets are kept: horse, snake, rat, hamster, dog, pony
 1. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
 3. the fan of d&b is not the owner of the dog##6
 4. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
 5. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 6. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 7. the owner of the dog is not the fan of classical##6
 8. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of funk is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the fan of rock##7
10. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
11. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
13. the owner of the horse is the fan of funk##1
14. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
15. the fan of salsa is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | funk | hip-hop   | salsa     | classical    | d&b   |
| Pet           | dog | horse   | pony | hamster | rat | snake |

