.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, crime, sports, animation, thriller
6 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, pony, hedgehog, ferret, hamster
 1. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
 7. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching animation movies is not the owner of the ferret##6
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the hedgehog##7
11. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
12. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
13. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
14. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
15. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
16. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
17. the person watching sports movies is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the person watching animation movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | thriller | sports | animation     | crime      | mystery |
| Pet           | frog         | pony        | ferret   | hedgehog | goldfish | hamster    |

