.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, mirinda, sprite, juice, iced-tea
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skateboarding, iced-tea-polo, climbing, golf, tennis, handball
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
 4. the person who's sport is iced-tea-polo is not the person drinking sprite##6
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
 6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 7. the person who's sport is iced-tea-polo is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
10. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking fanta##7
11. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
13. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
14. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | juice        | sprite | iced-tea    | almond-milk    | mirinda | fanta |
| Sport      | iced-tea-polo | tennis  | handball | golf | skateboarding | climbing      |

