.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, iced-tea, coffee, fanta, milk
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, comedy, zombie, disaster, martial-arts
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 3. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is not the person drinking fanta##6
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking fanta##7
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking milk##7
 8. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking coffee##7
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
13. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Beverage      | coffee | tea | milk | iced-tea | fanta | juice   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | zombie      | scientific | disaster     | martial-arts | musical |

