 4. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 5. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
 6. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person driving the roller##2
 7. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 9. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
11. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
12. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the person driving the ship##7
13. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | fish   | chinchilla | horse      | frog | hamster  | goat   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | subway  | ship | roller   | taxi | helicopter |

