.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: hiking, filmmaking, board-games, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku
The people have 6 different jobs:  software-developer, nurse, mechanic, chef, librarian, bartender
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the chef and the nurse##7
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the librarian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
 8. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
10. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
11. the bartender is on the right of the mechanic##1
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
14. the nurse is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
15. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | board-games         | magic-tricks | filmmaking | hiking   | sudoku | rock-climbing  |
| Job     | librarian | chef  | mechanic  | bartender | nurse  | software-developer |

 